[{"id": 606475, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1708, "text": "Elif, L\u00e2m, M\u00eem, R\u00e2. O Kitap'\u0131n ayetleridir bunlar. Ve sana Rabbinden indirilen, hakt\u0131r. Ne var ki, insanlar\u0131n \u00e7oklar\u0131 iman etmezler."}, {"id": 606476, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1709, "text": "Allah odur ki, g\u00f6kleri direksiz y\u00fckseltmi\u015ftir; g\u00f6r\u00fcyorsunuz onlar\u0131... Sonra ar\u015f \u00fczerine egemen olmu\u015ftur. G\u00fcne\u015f'i ve Ay'\u0131 da boyun e\u011fdirmi\u015ftir. Bunlar\u0131n t\u00fcm\u00fc belirlenmi\u015f bir vakte kadar akar dururlar. Olu\u015fu y\u00f6nlendirir, \u00e7ekip \u00e7evirir O... Ayetleri birer birer g\u00f6zler \u00f6n\u00fcne serer ki, Rabbinize kavu\u015faca\u011f\u0131n\u0131za a\u00e7\u0131k-se\u00e7ik inanas\u0131n\u0131z."}, {"id": 606477, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1710, "text": "Yeri uzat\u0131p d\u00f6\u015feyen ve onda oturakl\u0131 da\u011flar ve nehirler v\u00fccuda getiren O'dur. B\u00fct\u00fcn meyvelerden kendi i\u00e7lerinde iki\u015fer \u00e7ift yaratm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r O. Geceyi g\u00fcnd\u00fcze sar\u0131p b\u00fcr\u00fcmektedir O. B\u00fct\u00fcn bunlarda derin derin d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnecek bir topluluk i\u00e7in elbette ayetler vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 606478, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 99, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1711, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde birbirine s\u0131rt vermi\u015f kom\u015fu k\u0131talar, \u00fcz\u00fcmlerden bah\u00e7eler, ekinler, \u00e7atall\u0131 ve \u00e7atals\u0131z hurmal\u0131klar vard\u0131r ki, bir tek suyla sulan\u0131rlar. Biz bunlar\u0131n, yemi\u015flerde bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 di\u011fer bir k\u0131sm\u0131na \u00fcst\u00fcn k\u0131ld\u0131k. B\u00fct\u00fcn bunlarda akl\u0131n\u0131 \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131ran bir topluluk i\u00e7in elbette ki ibretler vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 606479, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 249, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1712, "text": "E\u011fer \u015fa\u015f\u0131yorsan, esas \u015fa\u015f\u0131lacak olan onlar\u0131n \u015fu s\u00f6z\u00fcd\u00fcr: \"Biz toprak olunca m\u0131 ve ger\u00e7ekten mi yeni bir yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f i\u00e7inde bulunaca\u011f\u0131z?\" Bunlar Rablerini ink\u00e2r edenlerdir. Ve bunlar boyunlar\u0131na buka\u011f\u0131lar vurulanlard\u0131r. Bunlar ate\u015fe dost olanlar\u0131n ta kendileridir; orada uzun s\u00fcre kalacaklard\u0131r."}, {"id": 606480, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1713, "text": "Senden, g\u00fczellikten \u00f6nce k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fck istemede acele ediyorlar. Halbuki \u00f6nlerinden pek \u00e7ok \u00f6rnek gelip ge\u00e7ti. \u015eu da bir ger\u00e7ek ki, Rabbin insanlara kar\u015f\u0131, zul\u00fcmlerine ra\u011fmen af sahibidir. Ve Rabbinin azab\u0131 elbette \u00e7ok \u015fiddetlidir."}, {"id": 606481, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 205, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1714, "text": "K\u00fcfre sapm\u0131\u015f olanlar \u015f\u00f6yle derler: \"Ona Rabbinden bir mucize indirilseydi ya!\" Sen sadece bir uyar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n ve her topluluk i\u00e7in do\u011fruyu ve iyiyi g\u00f6steren bir \u00f6nder vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 606482, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1715, "text": "Allah her di\u015finin neye gebe oldu\u011funu, rahimlerin neyi eksiltip neyi art\u0131raca\u011f\u0131 bilir. O'nun kat\u0131nda her \u015fey bir \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fcye ba\u011fl\u0131d\u0131r."}, {"id": 606483, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1716, "text": "Gayb\u0131 da g\u00f6r\u00fcnen \u00e2lemi de bilendir/\u00c2lim'dir O... Keb\u00eer, s\u0131n\u0131rs\u0131zca b\u00fcy\u00fck O'dur; M\u00fcte\u00e2l, sonsuzca y\u00fcce O'dur."}, {"id": 606484, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1717, "text": "Sizden, s\u00f6z\u00fc saklayan da a\u00e7\u0131klayan da geceye s\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131p gizlenen de g\u00fcnd\u00fcz yol alan da onun i\u00e7in birdir."}, {"id": 606485, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1718, "text": "Her biri i\u00e7in onu \u00f6n\u00fcnden ve arkas\u0131ndan izleyen g\u00f6zc\u00fcler vard\u0131r ki, kendisini Allah'\u0131n emrine ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak koruyup denetlerler. Ger\u00e7ek \u015fu ki Allah, bir toplumun m\u00e2ruz kald\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u015feyleri, onlar, birey olarak i\u00e7lerindekini/birey olarak kendilerine ili\u015fkin olan\u0131 de\u011fi\u015ftirmedik\u00e7e, de\u011fi\u015ftirmez. Allah bir topluma bir peri\u015fanl\u0131k dileyince de art\u0131k onu geri \u00e7evirecek bir g\u00fc\u00e7 yoktur. Ve onlar i\u00e7in Allah'\u0131n berisinden koruyucu bir dost da olamaz."}, {"id": 606486, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1719, "text": "Size, hem korku hem \u00fcmit olsun diye \u015fim\u015fe\u011fi g\u00f6steren O'dur. Y\u00fckl\u00fc y\u00fckl\u00fc bulutlar\u0131 da O olu\u015fturuyor."}, {"id": 606487, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 250, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1720, "text": "G\u00f6k g\u00fcr\u00fclt\u00fcs\u00fc O'nu hamd ile tespih eder; melekler de O'ndan \u00fcrpererek... Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131mlar g\u00f6nderir de onlarla diledi\u011fini \u00e7arpar. Allah, tuzak kuranlar\u0131n hilelerini ba\u015flar\u0131na ge\u00e7irmede \u00e7ok g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc oldu\u011fu halde, onlar O'na kar\u015f\u0131 m\u00fccadele edip duruyorlar."}, {"id": 606488, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1721, "text": "Ger\u00e7ek dua yaln\u0131z O'na/hak davet yaln\u0131z O'nun i\u00e7in yap\u0131l\u0131r. O'nun d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda yalvar\u0131p davet ettikleri ise onlara hi\u00e7bir \u015fekilde cevap veremezler. Onlar, a\u011fz\u0131na ula\u015fs\u0131n diye iki avucunu suya do\u011fru a\u00e7an ama suya ula\u015famayan birinden ba\u015fkas\u0131na benzemiyorlar. K\u00fcfre sapanlar\u0131n dua ve davetleri, \u015fa\u015fk\u0131nl\u0131\u011fa dalmaktan ba\u015fka bir i\u015fe yaramaz."}, {"id": 606489, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": true, "sajda_id": 2, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": true, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1722, "text": "G\u00f6klerde ve yerde kim varsa g\u00f6lgeleriyle birlikte ister istemez ve sabah-ak\u015fam Allah'a secde eder."}, {"id": 606490, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1723, "text": "De ki: \"G\u00f6klerin ve yerin Rabbi kim?\" De ki: \"Allah.\" De ki: \"O'nun yan\u0131nda ba\u015fka evliya m\u0131/destek\u00e7iler mi edindiniz? Bunlar kendilerine bile yarar sa\u011flay\u0131p zarar verme g\u00fcc\u00fcnde de\u011filler.\" De ki: \"K\u00f6rle g\u00f6ren yahut karanl\u0131klarla \u0131\u015f\u0131k bir olur mu? Yoksa Allah'a, t\u0131pk\u0131 O'nun yaratt\u0131\u011f\u0131 gibi yaratan ortaklar buldular da yarat\u0131\u015f/yarat\u0131lanlar kendileri i\u00e7in benze\u015fir hale mi geldi?\" De ki: \"Allah't\u0131r her \u015feyi yaratan, O'dur V\u00e2hid ve Kahh\u00e2r olan.\""}, {"id": 606491, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1724, "text": "G\u00f6kten bir su indirdi de vadiler, kendi \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fclerince/kaderlerine g\u00f6re sel oldu, ard\u0131ndan da sel, \u00fcste \u00e7\u0131kan k\u00f6p\u00fc\u011f\u00fc ta\u015f\u0131r hale geldi. Bir s\u00fcs e\u015fyas\u0131 veya \u00e2let yapmak iste\u011fiyle ate\u015fte k\u00f6r\u00fckledikleri \u015feylerde de benzeri bir k\u00f6p\u00fck vard\u0131r. Allah hakla b\u00e2t\u0131l\u0131 i\u015fte b\u00f6yle \u00f6rneklendiriyor: K\u00f6p\u00fck, at\u0131l\u0131r gider; insanlara yararl\u0131 olansa toprakta kal\u0131r. Allah, i\u015fte bu \u015fekilde \u00f6rnekler verir."}, {"id": 606492, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 251, "ruku": 206, "hizb_quarter": 100, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1725, "text": "Rablerinin \u00e7a\u011fr\u0131s\u0131na olumlu cevap verenler i\u00e7in g\u00fczellik vard\u0131r. O'na olumlu cevap vermeyenlere gelince, yery\u00fcz\u00fcndekilerin tamam\u0131 onlar\u0131n olsa, bir o kadar da ilave edilse, kurtulmak i\u00e7in bunlar\u0131n t\u00fcm\u00fcn\u00fc fidye verirlerdi. B\u00f6ylelerinin hesab\u0131 k\u00f6t\u00fc olacakt\u0131r; varacaklar\u0131 yer de cehennemdir. Ne k\u00f6t\u00fc yatakt\u0131r o!"}, {"id": 606493, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1726, "text": "Rabbinden sana indirilenin hak oldu\u011funu bilen ki\u015fi, k\u00f6r olan biriyle ayn\u0131 m\u0131d\u0131r? Sadece akl\u0131 ve g\u00f6nl\u00fc i\u015fleyenler d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcn\u00fcp ibret al\u0131r."}, {"id": 606494, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1727, "text": "\u0130\u015fte bunlard\u0131r, Allah'a verdikleri s\u00f6ze sad\u0131k kalanlar ve antla\u015fmay\u0131 bozmayanlar."}, {"id": 606495, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1728, "text": "Onlar, Allah'\u0131n ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 emretti\u011fi \u015feyi ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131rlar, Rablerinden korkarlar ve hesab\u0131n k\u00f6t\u00fcs\u00fcnden \u00fcrperti duyarlar."}, {"id": 606496, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1729, "text": "Onlar, Rablerinin y\u00fcz\u00fcn\u00fc arzulayarak sabrederler, namaz\u0131/duay\u0131 yerine getirirler, kendilerine verdi\u011fimiz r\u0131z\u0131klardan gizli ve a\u00e7\u0131k da\u011f\u0131t\u0131rlar ve k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc g\u00fczellikle savarlar. \u0130\u015fte bunlar i\u00e7indir s\u00fcrekli yurt."}, {"id": 606497, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1730, "text": "Adn cennetleri bunlar i\u00e7indir. Atalar\u0131ndan, e\u015flerinden, z\u00fcrriyetlerinden hayra ve bar\u0131\u015fa hizmet etmi\u015f olanlarla birlikte girerler oraya. Meleklerse her kap\u0131dan yanlar\u0131na sokulurlar."}, {"id": 606498, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1731, "text": "\"Selam size, sabretti\u011finiz i\u00e7in! Ne g\u00fczeldir \u015fu sonsuzluk yurdu!\" derler."}, {"id": 606499, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1732, "text": "Allah'a verdikleri s\u00f6z\u00fc, onu antla\u015fma haline getirdikten sonra bozanlar, Allah'\u0131n birle\u015ftirilmesini emretti\u011fi \u015feyi par\u00e7alayanlar ve yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bozgun \u00e7\u0131karanlara gelince, b\u00f6yleleri i\u00e7in lanet var. Yurdun en k\u00f6t\u00fcs\u00fc de onlar\u0131n olacak."}, {"id": 606500, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 207, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1733, "text": "Allah, diledi\u011fi kimse i\u00e7in r\u0131zk\u0131 alabildi\u011fine a\u00e7ar da s\u0131n\u0131rlay\u0131p k\u0131sar da. \u0130\u011freti d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131yla sevinip \u015f\u0131mard\u0131lar. Oysaki d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131, \u00e2hirete oranla sadece k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck bir nimetlenme."}, {"id": 606501, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1734, "text": "K\u00fcfre sapanlar derler ki: \"Rabbinden ona bir mucize indirilseydi ya!\" De ki: \"Allah diledi\u011fini/dileyeni sapt\u0131r\u0131r. Do\u011fruya y\u00f6neleni de kendisine iletir.\""}, {"id": 606502, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 252, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1735, "text": "B\u00f6yleleri, inanan ve g\u00f6n\u00fclleri Allah'\u0131n zikriyle/Kur'an'\u0131yla tatmin bulan ki\u015filerdir. G\u00f6z\u00fcn\u00fcz\u00fc a\u00e7\u0131n! G\u00f6n\u00fcller yaln\u0131z Allah'\u0131n zikriyle/Kur'an'la tatmin bulur."}, {"id": 606503, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1736, "text": "\u0130man edip hak ve bar\u0131\u015f u\u011fruna iyi i\u015fler yapanlara mutluluk ve m\u00fcjde var, g\u00fczel bir gelecek var."}, {"id": 606504, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1737, "text": "\u0130\u015fte seni b\u00f6ylece, kendilerinden \u00f6nce nice \u00fcmmetlerin gelip ge\u00e7ti\u011fi bir \u00fcmmet i\u00e7inde resul k\u0131ld\u0131k ki, onlar Rahman'a k\u00fcfrederlerken sen kendilerine, sana vahyetti\u011fimizi okuyas\u0131n. De ki: \"O'dur benim Rabbim, ilah yok O'ndan ba\u015fka, O'na dayanm\u0131\u015f\u0131m ben! Yaln\u0131z O'nad\u0131r t\u00f6vbem!\""}, {"id": 606505, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 208, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1738, "text": "Kendisiyle, da\u011flar\u0131n y\u00fcr\u00fct\u00fcld\u00fc\u011f\u00fc yahut yerk\u00fcrenin par\u00e7aland\u0131\u011f\u0131 yahut \u00f6l\u00fclerin konu\u015fturuldu\u011fu bir Kur'an m\u0131 olsayd\u0131! Hay\u0131r, i\u015f ve olu\u015fun t\u00fcm\u00fc Allah'\u0131nd\u0131r. \u0130man edenler h\u00e2l\u00e2 \u00fcmidi kesip anlamad\u0131lar m\u0131 ki, Allah dileseydi elbette insanlara t\u00fcmden hidayet verirdi. O k\u00fcfre sapanlara gelince, sanayi olarak \u00fcrettiklerinin sonucu halinde ba\u015flar\u0131na g\u00fclle-tokmak t\u00fcr\u00fcnden belalar inmeye devam edecek yahut o belalar onlar\u0131n yurtlar\u0131n\u0131n yak\u0131n\u0131na konacak. Ta, Allah'\u0131n vaadi gelinceye de\u011fin. Allah, vaadine asla ters d\u00fc\u015fmez."}, {"id": 606506, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1739, "text": "Yemin olsun, senden \u00f6nceki resullerle de alay edildi. \u0130nk\u00e2r edenlere biraz s\u00fcre verdim ama sonunda hepsini yakalad\u0131m. G\u00f6rd\u00fcler nas\u0131lm\u0131\u015f azap!"}, {"id": 606507, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1740, "text": "Allah'a ortaklar tan\u0131d\u0131lar. Peki, her benli\u011fin yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131 i\u015fin ba\u015f\u0131nda duranla bunlar bir mi? De ki: \"Onlar\u0131 isimlendirin. Yoksa siz Allah'a, yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde bilmedi\u011fi bir\u015fey mi haber veriyorsunuz? Yoksa, anlams\u0131z bir laf m\u0131 ediyorsunuz?\" Hay\u0131r, k\u00fcfre sapanlara, tuzaklar\u0131 s\u00fcsl\u00fc g\u00f6sterildi de yoldan d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcld\u00fcler. Allah'\u0131n \u015fa\u015f\u0131rtt\u0131\u011f\u0131na k\u0131lavuzluk edecek yok."}, {"id": 606508, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 253, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 101, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1741, "text": "D\u00fcnya hayat\u0131nda bir azap var onlar i\u00e7in; \u00e2hiret azab\u0131 ise \u00e7ok daha \u015fiddetlidir. Onlar\u0131 Allah'a kar\u015f\u0131 koruyacak kimse de yoktur."}, {"id": 606509, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1742, "text": "Sak\u0131n\u0131p korunanlara vaat edilen cennetin temsil\u00ee anlat\u0131m\u0131 \u015fu: Alt\u0131ndan \u0131rmaklar akar, yemi\u015fleri de s\u00fcrekli, g\u00f6lgesi de. \u0130\u015fte korunup sak\u0131nanlar\u0131n son yurdu. K\u00e2firlerin son yordu ise ate\u015f..."}, {"id": 606510, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1743, "text": "Kendilerine kitap verdiklerimiz, sana indirilenle ferahlarlar. Ama hiziplerden baz\u0131lar\u0131 onun bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 ink\u00e2r ederler. De ki: \"Bana, yaln\u0131z Allah'a kulluk etmem, O'na ortak ko\u015fmamam emredildi. Ben O'na yakar\u0131r, O'na davet ederim. D\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f\u00fcm de O'nad\u0131r.\""}, {"id": 606511, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 209, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1744, "text": "\u0130\u015fte biz o Kur'an'\u0131 Arap\u00e7a bir h\u00fck\u00fcm kayna\u011f\u0131 olarak indirdik. E\u011fer sana gelen ilimden sonra onlar\u0131n keyiflerine uyarsan, Allah'tan sana ne bir dost nasip olur ne de bir koruyucu."}, {"id": 606512, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1745, "text": "Yemin olsun, biz senden \u00f6nce de resuller g\u00f6nderdik, onlara da e\u015fler ve evlatlar verdik. Hi\u00e7bir resul, Allah'\u0131n izni olmad\u0131k\u00e7a herhangi bir mucize getiremez. Her s\u00fcre/s\u00fcre\u00e7 i\u00e7in bir kitap vard\u0131r."}, {"id": 606513, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1746, "text": "Allah diledi\u011fini silip yok eder, diledi\u011fini s\u00e2bit tutar. Kitap'\u0131n anas\u0131/ana Kitap O'nun kat\u0131ndad\u0131r."}, {"id": 606514, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1747, "text": "Ya onlara vaat etti\u011fimiz \u015feylerin bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 sana g\u00f6steririz yahut da seni vefat ettiririz. O halde tebli\u011f etmek sana, hesap sormak bize d\u00fc\u015fer."}, {"id": 606515, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1748, "text": "G\u00f6rm\u00fcyorlar m\u0131 ki biz o yerk\u00fcreye geliyor, onu u\u00e7lar\u0131ndan eksiltiyoruz. Allah h\u00fckmeder; O'nun h\u00fckm\u00fcn\u00fc denetleyecek de yoktur. Hesab\u0131 \u00e7ok \u00e7abuk g\u00f6r\u00fcr O."}, {"id": 606516, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 254, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1749, "text": "Onlardan \u00f6ncekiler de tuzak kurmu\u015ftu, ama t\u00fcm tuzaklar Allah'\u0131nd\u0131r. Her benli\u011fin ne kazand\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 O bilir. K\u00e2firler de bilecek sonsuzluk yurdu kimindir!"}, {"id": 606517, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 13, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u062f", "surah_en_name": "Ar-Ra'd", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Thunder", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 13, "manzil": 3, "page": 255, "ruku": 210, "hizb_quarter": 102, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 1750, "text": "K\u00fcfre sapanlar: \"Sen g\u00f6nderilmi\u015f bir el\u00e7i de\u011filsin.\" diyorlar. De ki: \"Benimle sizin aran\u0131zda tan\u0131k olarak Allah, bir de yan\u0131nda kitap bilgisi bulunanlar yeter.\""}]